snippet: Jimmy Walker and Jordan Spieth were tied at nine under par going into the third round of the AT&T Pebble Beach National Pro-Am in California on Friday.
abstract: Jimmy Walker and Jordan Spieth share second-round lead at the AT&T Pebble Beach National Pro-Am in California; other golf news noted.
